<h2>Step 3: Set Up AI Referral Traffic Tracking</h2>
<p>AI referral traffic is the one metric you can track for free right now with tools you already have.</p>
<h3>3A. Google Analytics 4</h3>
<p>In GA4, go to Reports &gt; Acquisition &gt; Traffic Acquisition. Look for these referral sources:</p>
